                      alt="image-20230623132750445"
                ></p>
<p><img  
                     lazyload
                     src="/images/loading.svg"
                     data-src="/images/vim/image-20230623133005272.png"
                      alt="image-20230623133005272"
                ></p>
<h3 id="2-操作符和动作"><a href="#2-操作符和动作" class="headerlink" title="2. 操作符和动作"></a>2. 操作符和动作</h3><p><img  
                     lazyload
